original_text:
ProbTimes = yearfrac(Settle,ProbData(:,1));
figure
plot([0; ProbTimes],[0; ProbData(:,2)])
grid on
axis([0 ProbTimes(end,1) 0 ProbData(end,2)])
xlabel('Time (Years)')
ylabel('Cumulative Default Probability')
title('Bootstrapped Default Probability Curve')
